<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Trainova — El gym en tu bolsillo</title>
  <meta name="description" content="La app para entrenadores personales y sus clientes. Rutinas, seguimiento y comunicación — todo en un solo lugar." />
  <meta property="og:title" content="Trainova — El gym en tu bolsillo" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Construye rutinas, sigue el progreso y comunícate con tus clientes. Disponible en App Store." />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; }

    /* ── Animated gradient orbs ────────────────────────── */
    .orb {
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 50%;
      filter: blur(80px);
      pointer-events: none;
      animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    .orb-1 {
      width: 500px; height: 500px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(108,99,255,0.18), transparent 70%);
      top: -150px; left: -100px;
      animation-delay: 0s;
    }
    .orb-2 {
      width: 400px; height: 400px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(78,205,196,0.15), transparent 70%);
      top: 0; right: -80px;
      animation-delay: -3s;
    }
    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
      50%       { transform: translateY(-24px); }
    }

    /* ── Hero layout ───────────────────────────────────── */
    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-2xl);
      align-items: center;
    }
    @media (max-width: 780px) {
      .hero-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .hero-grid .hero-actions { justify-content: center; }
      .phone-wrap { display: flex; justify-content: center; }
    }

    /* ── Phone mockup ──────────────────────────────────── */
    .phone {
      width: 220px;
      height: 440px;
      background: var(--surface);
      border-radius: 36px;
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 40px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.6), 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    }
    .phone::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 14px; left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 60px; height: 8px;
      background: var(--border);
      border-radius: 4px;
      z-index: 10;
    }
    .phone-screen {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 28px 0 0;
      padding: 16px 14px 14px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .phone-header {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .phone-title {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }
    .phone-card {
      background: var(--surface-raised);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 12px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .phone-card-label {
      font-size: 9px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .phone-card-value {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }
    .phone-exercise-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 8px 10px;
      background: var(--surface-raised);
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .phone-exercise-name { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); }
    .phone-exercise-sets { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-secondary); }
    .phone-pill {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(108,99,255,0.2);
      color: var(--accent-purple);
      font-size: 9px;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 2px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
    }
    .phone-btn {
      background: var(--gradient);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      margin-top: auto;
    }

    .phone-float {
      position: relative;
    }
    .phone-float .phone-2 {
      position: absolute;
      top: 40px;
      left: 140px;
      width: 180px;
      height: 360px;
      opacity: 0.6;
      transform: rotate(6deg);
    }

    /* ── How it works ──────────────────────────────────── */
    .how-it-works {
      padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .steps-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: var(--space-xl);
      position: relative;
    }
    .steps-grid::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 28px;
      left: calc(16.66% + 20px);
      right: calc(16.66% + 20px);
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--border), transparent);
    }
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .steps-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .steps-grid::before { display: none; }
    }
    .step-item { text-align: center; padding: 0 var(--space-sm); }
    .step-icon-wrap {
      width: 56px; height: 56px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.375rem;
      margin: 0 auto var(--space-md);
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .step-item h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: var(--space-xs); }
    .step-item p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; }

    /* ── Split showcase ────────────────────────────────── */
    .showcase {
      padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .showcase-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 2px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .showcase-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
    .showcase-panel {
      padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-xl);
      background: var(--surface);
    }
    .showcase-panel:first-child { border-right: 1px solid var(--border); }
    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .showcase-panel:first-child { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    }
    .showcase-panel .role-pill { margin-bottom: var(--space-md); }
    .showcase-panel h3 {
      font-size: 1.375rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    }
    .showcase-panel > p {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 0.9375rem;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    /* ── Social proof bar ──────────────────────────────── */
    .proof-bar {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
    }
    .proof-inner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: var(--space-3xl);
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .proof-stat { text-align: center; }
    .proof-stat strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      background: var(--gradient);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }
    .proof-stat span { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }

    /* ── Sticky mobile CTA ─────────────────────────────── */
    .sticky-cta {
      display: none;
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
      background: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      z-index: 200;
    }
    @media (max-width: 640px) { .sticky-cta { display: block; } }
    .sticky-cta .btn-primary { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }

    /* ── Testimonial ───────────────────────────────────── */
    .testimonials {
      padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .testimonials-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: var(--space-lg);
    }
    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .testimonials-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
    .testimonial-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      padding: var(--space-xl);
    }
    .testimonial-stars { color: var(--warning); font-size: 0.875rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-md); }
    .testimonial-card blockquote {
      font-size: 0.9375rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .testimonial-author { font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; }
    .testimonial-role { font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Nav -->
  <nav>
    <div class="container nav-inner">
      <span class="nav-logo gradient-text">Trainova</span>
      <a href="<%= appStoreUrl %>" class="nav-cta">Descargar gratis</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ── Hero ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="hero" style="padding: 80px 0 64px; overflow: visible;">
    <div class="orb orb-1"></div>
    <div class="orb orb-2"></div>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-grid">
        <!-- Copy -->
        <div>
          <div class="hero-badge" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);">
            <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12"><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="5" fill="#4ECDC4" opacity="0.3"/><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="3" fill="#4ECDC4"/></svg>
            <span>iOS 17+</span> · Gratis en App Store
          </div>

          <h1 style="text-align:left; font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5.5vw, 3.75rem);">
            El gym en<br/>
            <span class="gradient-text">tu bolsillo.</span>
          </h1>

          <p style="text-align:left; margin: var(--space-lg) 0 var(--space-xl); font-size:1.0625rem;">
            Para entrenadores que quieren crecer su negocio y clientes que quieren ver resultados. Rutinas, seguimiento y comunicación — todo en un solo lugar.
          </p>

          <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content: flex-start;">
            <a href="<%= appStoreUrl %>" class="appstore-badge">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18.71 19.5c-.83 1.24-1.71 2.45-3.05 2.47-1.34.03-1.77-.79-3.29-.79-1.53 0-2 .77-3.27.82-1.31.05-2.3-1.32-3.14-2.53C4.25 17 2.94 12.45 4.7 9.39c.87-1.52 2.43-2.48 4.12-2.51 1.28-.02 2.5.87 3.29.87.78 0 2.26-1.07 3.8-.91.65.03 2.47.26 3.64 1.98-.09.06-2.17 1.28-2.15 3.81.03 3.02 2.65 4.03 2.68 4.04-.03.07-.42 1.44-1.38 2.83M13 3.5c.73-.83 1.94-1.46 2.94-1.5.13 1.17-.34 2.35-1.04 3.19-.69.85-1.83 1.51-2.95 1.42-.15-1.15.41-2.35 1.05-3.11z"/></svg>
              Descargar en App Store
            </a>
            <span style="font-size:0.8125rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">Gratis · iOS 17+</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Phone mockup -->
        <div class="phone-wrap">
          <div class="phone-float">
            <!-- Back phone (trainer dashboard) -->
            <div class="phone phone-2" style="position:absolute; top:40px; left:150px; transform:rotate(6deg); opacity:0.55;">
              <div class="phone-screen">
                <div class="phone-header">Dashboard</div>
                <div class="phone-title">Tus clientes</div>
                <div class="phone-card">
                  <div class="phone-card-label">Esta semana</div>
                  <div style="display:flex; gap:6px; margin-top:6px;">
                    <div style="flex:1; background:rgba(108,99,255,0.3); border-radius:6px; height:36px; display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center; font-size:10px; font-weight:700; color:var(--accent-purple);">4/5</div>
                    <div style="flex:1; background:rgba(78,205,196,0.15); border-radius:6px; height:36px; display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center; font-size:10px; font-weight:700; color:var(--accent-teal);">87%</div>
                    <div style="flex:1; background:rgba(0,230,118,0.1); border-radius:6px; height:36px; display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center; font-size:10px; font-weight:700; color:var(--success);">↑12%</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="phone-exercise-row"><span class="phone-exercise-name">María G.</span><span class="phone-pill">Completo</span></div>
                <div class="phone-exercise-row"><span class="phone-exercise-name">Carlos R.</span><span style="font-size:9px; color:var(--warning);">Pendiente</span></div>
                <div class="phone-exercise-row"><span class="phone-exercise-name">Sofía L.</span><span class="phone-pill">Completo</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Front phone (client workout) -->
            <div class="phone">
              <div class="phone-screen">
                <div class="phone-header">Hoy · Lunes</div>
                <div class="phone-title">Empezar rutina</div>
                <div class="phone-card">
                  <div class="phone-card-label">Fuerza — Pierna</div>
                  <div class="phone-card-value">6 ejercicios · ~50 min</div>
                </div>
                <div class="phone-exercise-row">
                  <div>
                    <div class="phone-exercise-name">Sentadilla</div>
                    <div class="phone-exercise-sets">4 × 8 · 80 kg</div>
                  </div>
                  <span style="color:var(--success); font-size:14px;">✓</span>
                </div>
                <div class="phone-exercise-row">
                  <div>
                    <div class="phone-exercise-name">Peso muerto</div>
                    <div class="phone-exercise-sets">3 × 6 · 100 kg</div>
                  </div>
                  <span style="color:var(--success); font-size:14px;">✓</span>
                </div>
                <div class="phone-exercise-row" style="border-color: var(--accent-purple); background: rgba(108,99,255,0.08);">
                  <div>
                    <div class="phone-exercise-name">Prensa</div>
                    <div class="phone-exercise-sets">4 × 10 · 120 kg</div>
                  </div>
                  <span style="color:var(--accent-purple); font-size:14px;">▶</span>
                </div>
                <div class="phone-btn">Registrar serie →</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Proof bar ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <div class="proof-bar">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="proof-inner">
        <div class="proof-stat"><strong>2 tap</strong><span>para registrar una serie</span></div>
        <div class="proof-stat"><strong>∞</strong><span>ejercicios en biblioteca</span></div>
        <div class="proof-stat"><strong>iOS</strong><span>nativo · sin web lenta</span></div>
        <div class="proof-stat"><strong>MX</strong><span>hecho para México</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── How it works ───────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="how-it-works">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">Así funciona</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">De cero a entrenando en minutos.</h2>

      <div class="steps-grid">
        <div class="step-item">
          <div class="step-icon-wrap" style="background: rgba(108,99,255,0.1); border-color: rgba(108,99,255,0.3);">🏋️</div>
          <h3>Entrenador crea la rutina</h3>
          <p>Elige ejercicios de la biblioteca, define series, peso y descanso. O pídele a la IA que la genere.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-item">
          <div class="step-icon-wrap" style="background: rgba(78,205,196,0.1); border-color: rgba(78,205,196,0.3);">📩</div>
          <h3>Invita a tu cliente</h3>
          <p>Envía un enlace por WhatsApp o email. El cliente descarga la app y queda conectado contigo.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-item">
          <div class="step-icon-wrap" style="background: rgba(0,230,118,0.1); border-color: rgba(0,230,118,0.3);">📈</div>
          <h3>Sigue el progreso juntos</h3>
          <p>El cliente registra cada serie. Tú ves el cumplimiento en tiempo real y ajustas el plan.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Trainer vs Client showcase ────────────────────── -->
  <section class="showcase">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">Dos experiencias, una app</p>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);">Diseñada para los dos lados del entrenamiento.</h2>

      <div class="showcase-grid">
        <div class="showcase-panel">
          <span class="role-pill trainer">Para el entrenador</span>
          <h3>Gestiona tu negocio desde donde estés.</h3>
          <p>Deja de usar hojas de cálculo y mensajes de WhatsApp para coordinar con tus clientes. Trainova centraliza todo.</p>
          <ul class="role-list">
            <li>Dashboard de cumplimiento con anillos por cliente</li>
            <li>Constructor de rutinas y programas multi-semana</li>
            <li>Generación de rutinas con IA en segundos</li>
            <li>Biblioteca de ejercicios con video demostración</li>
            <li>Invita clientes por link o email</li>
            <li>Chat directo integrado</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="showcase-panel">
          <span class="role-pill client">Para el cliente</span>
          <h3>Enfócate en entrenar, no en buscar qué hacer.</h3>
          <p>Abre la app y ya sabes qué toca hoy. Sin buscar en mensajes ni recordar qué dijo tu entrenador.</p>
          <ul class="role-list">
            <li>Rutina del día visible al instante</li>
            <li>Registro de series con 2 taps y timer de descanso</li>
            <li>Video de cada ejercicio al alcance</li>
            <li>Historial de progreso y métricas corporales</li>
            <li>Logros y rachas que motivan la constancia</li>
            <li>Chat con tu entrenador sin salir de la app</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Testimonials ───────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="testimonials">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">Lo que dicen</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Entrenadores y clientes que ya lo usan.</h2>

      <div class="testimonials-grid">
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <blockquote>"Antes coordinaba todo por WhatsApp y era un caos. Con Trainova mis clientes saben exactamente qué hacer y yo veo en tiempo real quién cumplió."</blockquote>
          <div class="testimonial-author">Luis Mendoza</div>
          <div class="testimonial-role">Entrenador personal · CDMX</div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <blockquote>"Me encanta que apenas abro la app ya sé qué entreno hoy. No tengo que buscar nada ni recordar. Solo empiezo."</blockquote>
          <div class="testimonial-author">Andrea Torres</div>
          <div class="testimonial-role">Cliente · Guadalajara</div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <blockquote>"El generador de rutinas con IA me ahorra horas. Describes el objetivo y te da una rutina completa lista para asignar al cliente."</blockquote>
          <div class="testimonial-author">Roberto Sánchez</div>
          <div class="testimonial-role">Entrenador · Monterrey</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Final CTA ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-card">
        <div class="hero-badge" style="display:inline-flex; margin-bottom:var(--space-lg);">
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12"><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="5" fill="#4ECDC4" opacity="0.3"/><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="3" fill="#4ECDC4"/></svg>
          Disponible ahora · Gratis
        </div>
        <h2>Empieza a <span class="gradient-text">entrenar mejor</span> hoy.</h2>
        <p>Descarga Trainova gratis. Para iPhone con iOS 17 o superior.</p>
        <a href="<%= appStoreUrl %>" class="appstore-badge" style="display:inline-flex;">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18.71 19.5c-.83 1.24-1.71 2.45-3.05 2.47-1.34.03-1.77-.79-3.29-.79-1.53 0-2 .77-3.27.82-1.31.05-2.3-1.32-3.14-2.53C4.25 17 2.94 12.45 4.7 9.39c.87-1.52 2.43-2.48 4.12-2.51 1.28-.02 2.5.87 3.29.87.78 0 2.26-1.07 3.8-.91.65.03 2.47.26 3.64 1.98-.09.06-2.17 1.28-2.15 3.81.03 3.02 2.65 4.03 2.68 4.04-.03.07-.42 1.44-1.38 2.83M13 3.5c.73-.83 1.94-1.46 2.94-1.5.13 1.17-.34 2.35-1.04 3.19-.69.85-1.83 1.51-2.95 1.42-.15-1.15.41-2.35 1.05-3.11z"/></svg>
          Descargar en App Store
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer>
    <div class="container footer-inner">
      <span class="footer-logo gradient-text">Trainova</span>
      <ul class="footer-links">
        <li><a href="/privacy">Privacidad</a></li>
        <li><a href="mailto:hola@trainova.fit">Contacto</a></li>
      </ul>
      <span class="footer-copy">© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Trainova</span>
